---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import CTASection from '../../components/CTASection';
import Reviews from '../../components/Reviews';
import ServiceForm from '../../components/ServiceForm';
import LicenseBadges from '../../components/LicenseBadges.astro';
import BrandsSection from '../../components/BrandsSection.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="HVAC Services in Orange County, CA | HiLo Heating & Air" description="Expert AC repair, heating service, and HVAC maintenance throughout Orange County, CA. From coastal corrosion to inland heat, HiLo Heating & Air covers it all.">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-blue to-blue-800 py-20 sm:py-28">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">AC Repair Orange County</h1>
        <p class="text-white/80 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">Orange County stretches from coastal towns where salt air eats at outdoor units to inland neighborhoods where summer heat just sits and bakes everything for months. HiLo Heating and Air handles AC repair across that whole range.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <LicenseBadges />
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
          <div>
            <span class="inline-block bg-brand-blue/10 text-brand-blue text-sm font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-4">Schedule Service</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-brand-blue mb-4">Get a Free Estimate</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6">Fill out the form and our team will get back to you within 15 minutes. Same-day service available.</p>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-blue">Same-Day Service Available</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-blue">Free Diagnostics with Repair</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-blue" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 18.75a60.07 60.07 0 0115.797 2.101c.727.198 1.453-.342 1.453-1.096V18.75M3.75 4.5v.75A.75.75 0 013 6h-.75m0 0v-.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125H20.25M2.25 6v9m18-10.5v.75c0 .414.336.75.75.75h.75m-1.5-1.5h.375c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v9.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-.375m1.5-1.5H21a.75.75 0 00-.75.75v.75m0 0H3.75m0 0h-.375a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V15m1.5 1.5v-.75A.75.75 0 003 15h-.75M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm3 0h.008v.008H18V10.5zm-12 0h.008v.008H6V10.5z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-brand-blue">Upfront Pricing, No Hidden Fees</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ServiceForm client:load />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>



    <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 prose prose-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-brand-blue mt-0 mb-4">AC &amp; HVAC Services Across Orange County</h2>

        <p>Orange County stretches from coastal towns where salt air eats at outdoor units to inland neighborhoods where summer heat just sits and bakes everything for months. Different conditions, same end result — AC systems take a beating no matter where you live here. Hilo Heating and Air handles <strong>air conditioning repair Orange County</strong> homeowners need across that whole range, from Costa Mesa to Irvine to Rancho Santa Margarita and everywhere in between.</p>

        <h2>Why One Company Across So Many Cities Works Better</h2>
        <p>Calling around for a new HVAC company every time you move neighborhoods gets old fast. We cover the county broadly enough that most people just keep our number, regardless of which city they end up in. That consistency matters for <strong>air conditioning repair Orange County</strong> residents especially — same techs, same standards, same pricing approach whether you're a mile from the beach or twenty minutes inland.</p>

        <h2>What We're Usually Fixing</h2>
        <p>A handful of issues show up again and again — a capacitor that's finally given out, a coil thick with dust or, near the coast, corrosion, a refrigerant leak slowly tanking performance, or a compressor that's just old. That's most of what <strong>air conditioning repair Orange County</strong> calls turn into: weak airflow, a unit cycling too often, or one that won't start at all. We diagnose before quoting, because guessing wastes everyone's time and money.</p>

        <h2>We Get There Fast</h2>
        <p>A dead AC in August isn't something that can wait a week. Most repairs get same-day or next-day scheduling, with trucks stocked for the parts that fail most often in this region — which, depending on the city, sometimes means corrosion-related fixes, sometimes just general wear. Either way, most <strong>air conditioning repair Orange County</strong> jobs wrap up in a single visit.</p>

        <h2>Local Knowledge That Actually Helps</h2>
        <p>Covering this much territory means we've seen how different the climate and housing styles really are block to block — coastal corrosion in one area, older ductwork in another, newer builds somewhere else entirely. Every job's done to code and backed by a guarantee, no matter which Orange County neighborhood it's in.</p>
        <p>If your AC's struggling, give Hilo Heating and Air a call. We'd rather diagnose it properly the first time, wherever you're located.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    

    <Reviews client:visible />
    <BrandsSection />

    <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-slate-50">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-blue mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">What cities in Orange County do you actually cover?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">A wide range — Costa Mesa, Irvine, Newport Beach, Rancho Santa Margarita, Laguna Hills, and more. Just ask and we'll confirm your area.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">How fast can someone come out?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Usually same-day, sometimes next-day during busier periods.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Does location within the county change what's usually wrong with the AC?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Somewhat — coastal homes deal with more corrosion, inland homes deal with more general wear from heat. We adjust diagnostics accordingly.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Will I get pricing before work starts?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Yes, always upfront — no surprises on the bill.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">How often should the AC get inspected?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Once a year, ideally before summer hits.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Do you work on all brands and system types?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Yes — central air, mini-splits, heat pumps, most major brands.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">Are your technicians licensed and insured?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Every technician, fully licensed and insured.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-brand-blue/10">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand-blue mb-2">What if the problem comes back after a repair?</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Covered under our guarantee — just give us a call.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-brand-blue/5 py-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <p class="text-brand-blue font-semibold">HiLo Heating and Air · 8131 Electric Ave, Stanton, CA 90680, United States</p>
        <p class="text-slate-600 mt-1"><a href="tel:+17148535534" class="hover:text-brand-red transition">(714) 853-5534</a> · <a href="mailto:info@hiloheatingandair.com" class="hover:text-brand-red transition">info@hiloheatingandair.com</a></p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <CTASection client:visible />
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
